sources.description:
A man's life ticking away as a boy decides his fate!
An American gangster travels to Athens in search of his ex-wife, where he becomes entangled in a plot to obtain her family's fortune. And he involves his son in an attempt to harm his son's stepfather.

Original title: Nine Miles to Noon (1963)
This film has subtitles available in many language options.  

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/EtY41b-lA4Y


Director & Writer: Herbert J. Leder
Stars: Renato Baldini, Dolores Sutton, Peter Lazer & Nana Mouskouri
Genres: Colorized, Drama, Murder Mystery, Crime, Thriller
